Usage:
    format_opt_lists.pl : --doom=DOOM : [--help -? --usage] [--man]
    [--stuff=STUFF] : [--help -? --usage] [--man] --doom=DOOM
    [--stuff=STUFF]

Options:
     Required:
         --doom            - Int. 
     Optional:
         --help -? --usage - Bool. Display the usage message and exit
         --man             - Bool. Display man page
         --stuff           - String.

